<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>포켓몬 도감 - 회원가입 완료</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <img src="/image/pokemon_logo.png" alt="포켓몬 로고" class="logo">
        <h1>회원가입 완료</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="success-content">
        <div class="success-icon">✅</div>
        <h2>환영합니다!</h2>
        {{#userName}}
            <p><strong>{{userName}}</strong>님의 회원가입이 완료되었습니다.</p>
        {{/userName}}
        {{#successMessage}}
            <p class="success-message">{{successMessage}}</p>
        {{/successMessage}}

        <div class="action-buttons">
            <a href="/users/login" class="primary-btn">로그인하기</a>
            <a href="/" class="secondary-btn">홈으로 가기</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>포켓몬 도감에서 다양한 포켓몬을 만나보세요!</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>